nodes.text: This battle droid was stationed on Asajj Ventress's Trident-class assault ship during the Battle of Kamino along with a fellow droid.

Before the assault on Tipoca City, this battle droid accompanied Asajj Ventress on her Trident starship below the seas of Kamino in her infiltration mission. After the battle began, this droid informed Ventress that the reinforcement, which were disguised as starship debris, have landed in the sea.
The B1 battle droid, like every battle droid in The Clone Wars movie and The Clone Wars TV series, was voiced by Matthew Wood. His name was never given.
